SELECT distinct claimant.SystemId, claimant.ParentId, claimant.CMMContainer, claimant.Id, claimant.ClaimantNumber, claimant.ClaimantTypeCd, claimant.ClaimantSubTypeCd, claimant.Comment, claimant.StatusCd, claimant.StatusDt, claimant.InjuryDesc, claimant.MajorTraumaCd, claimant.FatalityInd, claimant.IndexName, claimant.PreferredDeliveryMethod, claimant.InjuryInvolvedInd, claimant.InjuredPartyRelationshipCd, claimant.MedicareReportingFilename, claimant.ClaimantLinkIdRef, claimant.ClaimantLinkDescription, claimant.PreferredPaymentMethodCd, claimant.InternationalInd, claimant.DeathDt, claimant.MMIDt, claimant.MMIPct, claimant.InjuredPartyContacted, claimant.NumberOfDependents, claimant.NatureCd, claimant.BodyPartGeneralCd, claimant.BodyPartSpecificCd, claimant.BodyPartIAIABCCd, claimant.InitialTreatment, claimant.DisabilityTypeCd, claimant.ClassCd, claimant.EmploymentStatusCd, claimant.ShiftCd, claimant.HourlySalaryCd, claimant.AverageWeeklyWagesAmt, claimant.HireDt, claimant.PayrollLocation, claimant.Department, claimant.LastWorkedDt, claimant.MealsLodging, claimant.InpatientOvernight, claimant.EmergencyRoomOnly, claimant.LiabilityDenied, claimant.LiabilityDeniedDesc, claimant.PaidFullWages, claimant.SalaryContinued, claimant.BenefitAmt, claimant.DeathBenefitAmt, claimant.DaysPaid, claimant.WeeksPaid, claimant.UpdateCount, claimant.UpdateUser, claimant.UpdateTimestamp, claimant.Status, claimant.BenefitRate, claimant.OverrideRate, claimant.OverrideRateComments, claimant.ShortDescription, claimant.DetailDescription, claimant.OccupationDescription, claimant.ManagedCareOrganizationTypeCd, claimant.EducationLevel, claimant.PreExistingDisabilityCd, claimant.ReducedBenefitAmountCd, claimant.AdjusterName, claimant.AdjusterCompany, claimant.AttorneyName, claimant.AttorneyFirm, claimant.PhoneNamePA, claimant.PhoneNumberPA, claimant.EmailAddrPA, claimant.PhoneNameAttorney, claimant.PhoneNumberAttorney, claimant.EmailAddrAttorney, claimant.AssignedAdjusterName 
FROM
  claimant where claimant.CMMContainer='Claim' and claimant.SystemId in (select systemid from advrxxchangedbeans where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' and
 cmmcontainer='Claim')

SELECT  n.CommercialName as IndexName, 
p.ProviderTypeCd as ProviderTypeCd, p.SystemId as SystemId,p.ProviderNumber as ProviderNumber
FROM 
provider p inner join nameinfo n on
p.systemid=n.systemid
where p.CMMContainer='Provider' 
and n.cmmcontainer='Provider'
and p.ProviderTypeCd='Outside Adjuster'
and n.nametypecd='ProviderName'
